{"tid":2133424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[瘋狂DQ] 當年少林足球 究竟係點打贏魔鬼隊？","createTime":"2020-07-31T05:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T07:03:03.000Z","uid":101392,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3f287f3d488531bd91f84c5f3117d8c79efd9b9b","tid":2133424,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZZgXOr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZZgXOr.jpg&h=65456d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家港共瘋狂DQ 就好似少林足球強雄咁<br />\n球證、旁證、主辦、協辦都係佢地嘅人<br />\n對家打曬茅波<br />\n我方球員一一被逼離場 <br />\n好似少林隊少過7個人就會自動判輸咁<br />\n<br />\n正常嚟講 面對咁唔公平嘅遊戲規則<br />\n唔應該繼續玩落去 應該拍檯走人<br />\n包括我尋日都開post贊成杯葛選舉<br />\n<br />\n但當年少林隊究竟點解繼續玩落去？<br />\n點解到頭來又贏到？<br />\n<br />\n雖然話係做戲姐 但都要有logic㗎 <br />\n理由點牽強都好都要作個理由俾佢"},{"pid":"7848ab8cd2c62d0294eee12cd05351adaacfc460","tid":2133424,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"我記得劇情好似係阿梅（趙薇）做後備上場 救世界<br />\n但明明球證係強雄嘅人<br />\n其實明明可以求其話佢太樣衰 跟住紅牌趕佢出場wor"},{"pid":"4801f673af64c5e158f7abab95cd28cacda1403e","tid":2133424,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"因為有個更勁嘅自己友出黎幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bced571f65a7ea7a1c4b9f6703192e5a44fb1f","tid":2133424,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4801f673af64c5e158f7abab95cd28cacda1403e","tid":2133424,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"因為有個更勁嘅自己友出黎幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"點解強雄唔叫球證DQ埋佢？唔太記得劇情"},{"pid":"6a040a35feccd057a5d4a80cd70ba11e875a5022","tid":2133424,"uid":15592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"因為強雄都冇咁無恥玩DQ"},{"pid":"7cc1e70195e9d79b15106e1d9479987db68acf50